songs.title: Keisha
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
So much to accomplish now
Don't be odd and don't be boring now
Catch appointments use tomorrow now
(Yeah, o-woah-ooo)
Don't be actin' prude and shit
I ain't out here tryna bool a bitch
Stand off, don't be rude and shit (o-woah-ooo)
Stand off, don't be rude and shit

[Pre-Chorus]
Don't let your inhibitions, get in your way
Time's of the essence, don't hesitate
On a multiple mission, take off on me (Oooo)
Fuckin' with a real one, keep my company

[Chorus]
Keisha, don't let me fall asleep, no
Keep an eye on me, no
Don't let me catch no Z's, no
Don't let me fall asleep, no
Keep an eye on me, no
Don't let me catch no Z's, no
Keisha, Keisha
Don't let me fall asleep, no

[Verse 2]
You selfish baby
Ain't no other way around it
Ooh, satisfy your appetite
Ain't no tappin' out, baby
Passion mark, put them scratches on my back
They ain't here baby, tell 'em handle that
Boomerang, you gon' keep on coming back
For more

[Pre-Chorus]
You could pick the location
Strap me up and put you on that flight
Take what's up from her make it alright
Ooo, I know you 'bout that life
Ooo, I know you 'bout that-

[Chorus]
Keisha, don't let me fall asleep, no
Keep an eye on me, no
Don't let me catch no Z's, no
Don't let me fall asleep, no
Keep an eye on me, no
Don't let me catch no Z's, no
Keisha, Keisha
Don't let me fall asleep, no
